ion="#langesS">s</c>s noch nicht am <date>19.</date> Vielleicht <date>23.</date> od <date>24. November</date>.)</p><closer>Herzlichst<lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur.</signed></closer></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb2121">
